      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/criteria/sqa-level2",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys 2022 R2, DePuy Synthes proprietary solver) operate under documented software quality assurance plans including version control, regression test suites, and change-control procedures. Ansys and DePuy Synthes codes hold ISO 9001 certification. FDA in-house code is covered under CDRH SQA policy v3.1. Required level 2 (documented SQA plan) is exceeded; achieved level 3 reflects independent regression testing across solver versions."
